headline.main: Team Sky's Kwiatkowski Wins Strade Bianche Classic
headline.print_headline: Team Sky's Kwiatkowski Wins Strade Bianche Classic

lead_paragraph: Team Sky found something to cheer about after a tough week off the road when former world champion Michal Kwiatkowski won the prestigious Strade Bianche classic on Saturday.
